'''Skull-Biters Flightknife''' was a unit of [[Adumari]] [[Blade series]] [[Starfighter/Legends|starfighters]] from the [[Planet/Legends|planet]] [[Adumar/Legends|Adumar]]. It participated in the [[Adumari Civil War]] and flew in defense of the [[Cartann]] nation.

They were the first flightknife to surrender to [[General/Legends|General]] [[Wedge Antilles/Legends|Wedge Antilles]] upon receiving the orders from the captured Cartann [[perator]].

